  "name": "Obliterate Memory",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/spells/light-royal-1.jpg",
  "sort": 0,
  "flags": {},
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a standard action, you can target a creature within 30 feet and eliminate all memory of an event the target experienced, as @Compendium[pf1.spells.5ll7q13p0skbgonc]{Modify Memory}. A target can attempt a Will save to negate this effect. In addition, you can cause an account of the memory erased by this ability to appear on a blank page of any book you are carrying.</p>\n<p>You can use this ability once per day, plus one additional time per day at 15th level.</p>\n<p>You must be at least 11th level to select this revelation.</p>"
    },
